HEADWORD: Spokesman
<hw>Spokes"man</hw> <pr>(sp⟦omac⟧ks"m⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Spokesmen</plw> <pr>(-m⟦eit⟧n)</pr>.</plu>
